title: NPC_1_Start
---
<<declare $trust = 0>>
<<declare $knows_secret = false>>

Traveler: Greetings, wanderer. These roads can be dangerous alone. #line:039436e 

-> Greet them warmly #line:02d837c 
    <<set $trust += 1>>
    Traveler: Indeed it is. Perhaps we could travel together a while? #line:0e988d4 
    <<jump TravelTogether>>
-> Eye them suspiciously #line:08a1519 
    Traveler: I'm sure you can. But even the strongest benefit from allies. #line:0c86dea 
    <<jump Suspicious>>
-> Ignore them and walk past #line:015d702 
    Traveler: Suit yourself... but beware the enemies ahead. #line:00bbfe6 
===
title: TravelTogether
---
Traveler: I should warn you—there's trouble at the old bridge. #line:00b9b98 

-> Ask for details #line:085841b 
    <<set $trust += 1>>
    Traveler: Bandits have been collecting "tolls." Unfair ones. #line:0e0914f 
    <<if $trust >= 2>>
        Traveler: I know a secret path, if you're interested... #line:085f8f2 
    <<else>>
        Traveler: But together, we might get through. #line:0a5f78f 
    <<endif>>
-> Say nothing #line:0275202 

===
title: Suspicious
---
Traveler: I understand caution. The world has earned it. #line:09f3514  #line:0e56abb 
Traveler: Here—take this. It shows a path around the bandits at the bridge. #line:00658bf 

-> Accept the map #line:0ae909e 
    Traveler: Safe travels. #line:04a80bd 
-> Refuse #line:056d8e3 
===
